               śrī-vi
<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ya-ma
<hi rend="grantha">hā</hi>rā
<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ṟku yāṇṭu
               
<lb n="2" break="no" />
<unclear>Eṭṭ-ā</unclear>vatu
            </p>
            
            
<p> puliyūr-k-kōṭṭattu-p pērūr-nāṭṭu
               
<lb n="3" />kuḷappākka-kiḻāṉ nātaṉ 
<unclear>tēva</unclear>
               
<lb n="4" break="no" />
<unclear>ṉ Iv</unclear>-vūr-t tiru-va
<hi rend="grantha">ha</hi>sti
<hi rend="grantha">sva</hi>rattu ma
<hi rend="grantha">hā</hi>tēvaṟkku Ā
               
<lb n="5" />cantira-kālamum nicamum matyāṉatt’ oru tiru-v-amirtuk
               
<lb n="6" break="no" />ku vaitta pūmi tūmpeṉappaṭṭikku mērki
               
<lb n="7" break="no" />ṟ kāṭṭu kuḷakkollai Iru-nūṟṟ’ aimpatu ku
               
<lb n="8" break="no" />ḻi
            </p>
            
            
<p>
               I-tarmmam ra
<hi rend="grantha">kṣi</hi>kka kaṭavōm Ūrom 
<surplus>Ūrōm</surplus>
            </p>
            
            
<p>itu panmā
               
<lb n="9" break="no" />he
<hi rend="grantha">sva</hi>rar ra
<hi rend="grantha">kṣai</hi></p>
            
            
<p>
               I-tarmmam ra
<hi rend="grantha">kṣi</hi>ppār pāta
               
<lb n="10" break="no" />
<gap reason="undefined" quantity="1" unit="line" />
               
<lb n="11" break="no" />tuḷ Eṉ talai mēḻaṉa
